---
title: Home
description: Homepage for Matthew Parris's personal website
changeFreq: weekly
---

{% extends "src/layouts/main-layout.njk" %}

{% block head %}
    {{ super() }}

    {% set css %}
        {% include "src/assets/styles/index.css" %}
        {% include "src/assets/styles/most-recent-post.css" %}
    {% endset %}

    <style>
        {{ css | cssmin | safe }}
    </style>
{% endblock %}

{% block content %}
    <section id="introduction-section">
        <header class="left">
            <div id="header-content">
                <img src="/img/header-avatar.jpg" id="header-avatar" alt="A not so professional headshot of Matthew">
            </div>
        </header>
        <div class="right">
            <h2>Hi, I'm Matthew</h2>

            <p>
                I've just recently graduated from the University of Tulsa with a degree in computer science.
                Right now, I am stuck at my house due to coronavirus.
            </p>

            <p>On here, I am writing about topics tangent to the important stuff.</p>
        </div>   
    </section>

    <section>
        <div class="left">
            <h2>Blog</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="right">
            {% include "src/includes/_most-recent-post.njk" %}
        </div>
    </section>
{% endblock %}